name: Reflection
description:
Maybe it's quite late, but I really want to celebrate and immortalize it here. Because this is entering the cycle of the third decade of my life. I am very grateful and this feeling is sufficient to represent myself, which is still given my breath until this moment. Everything starts with one and there is always a shadow.


One shadow, one life, always following every footstep. Being a protector and reflecting on the world in a different way to live life.

regards
Ranselusang
